{"tid":590094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【洗碗當畀錢】食客無錢畀 日本呢間食堂真係可以洗碗算","createTime":"2018-03-12T10:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T14:11:23.000Z","uid":75969,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ee2176eb9fbbd273a94be691583a5a1fb00e3ee7","tid":590094,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:25:12.000Z","msg":"「食飯冇錢畀就用洗碗代替」一直以來是餐飲業界的玩笑，但在日本東京這一間餐廳卻是事實。餐廳為讓沒有能力付錢的食客果腹，推出以工作50分鐘的勞力代替金錢，開業兩年已有逾500人「食飯冇畀錢」。<br />\n<br />\n位於東京神田神保町的未來食堂只有一位長期店員，就是33歲店主小林世界（Sekai Kobayashi音譯）。食堂在2016年開業，所提供的定食售價為900日圓（66港元），她為讓貧苦大眾可以用膳，便以工作50分鐘代替飯錢，早上的工作是協助接單和清理盤子，晚上則負責洗碗。<br />\n<br />\n小林過往是工程師，曾在美國商業機器（IBM）的日本分公司工作，她決心開餐廳是因為「同事很喜歡我煮的午餐，令我強烈考慮開餐廳」，她後來接受培訓及到餐廳實習後就自己開業。<br />\n<br />\n小林又會將餐廳的經營資料在互聯網上公開，讓其他有意創業者參考。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520758447_cd4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520758447_cd4e.jpg&h=ccdd1471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180312/57927931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F57927931&d=x9LhHYmcYY%2BSM2472jRuA8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6cff255a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F57927931&h=eaadcd0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180312/57927931</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果香港有餐廳咁做會點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190a947c1d50ea09a5c98e63139a1b465581082f","tid":590094,"uid":143171,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:26:55.000Z","msg":"一定成班廢佬狗衝 但hea做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e269e64e7